Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:04.98,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 真不可思议 为什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:12.76,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}你一笑起来 心里总会闪亮亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.81,0:12:15.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will step 一步一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.43,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Dest will skip 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:31.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}回过神来 发现已经着迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:36.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}"这种事会有的吧?" 你这样说道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:42.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}紧紧地握住我的手 体温传达给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.31,0:12:47.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}不管去哪里 都感觉无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:53.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tin ton tan 跨出那一步的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:58.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}世界就像全景画一样 展开了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:04.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 无论天空有多宽阔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:10.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}如果只有我一人 肯定不会在意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.16,0:13:15.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}Tinkling Smile 笑声回响在耳边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:23.05,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}心中充满温柔、愉悦的感觉 还有新的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:28.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(150,150)}一步 一步 前进吧
